Kalau nak bergaduh, pergi gaduh di luar.

493
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:08,720
Saya tak boleh tumpukan perhatian.

494
00:32:08,920 --> 00:32:10,510
Tolong tutup pintu sekali.

495
00:32:10,670 --> 00:32:11,750
Awaklah.

496
00:32:11,980 --> 00:32:12,980
Ya.

497
00:32:16,780 --> 00:32:18,230
Memandangkan awak teringin sangat nak pergi, cepatlah pergi.

498
00:32:18,230 --> 00:32:19,870
Jelas sekali tuan awak yang halau orang.

499
00:32:19,870 --> 00:32:22,600
Awak bukan tuan saya, kenapa nak marah saya pula?

500
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:41,920
Tugas saya, siasat apa yang sebenarnya berlaku kepada Klao yang sebenar.

501
00:32:52,800 --> 00:32:55,330
Bukan saya dah kata jangan masuk dulu, Chuay?

502
00:33:05,230 --> 00:33:08,200
Orang di dapur kata awak kurung diri dalam bilik sepanjang hari.

503
00:33:08,200 --> 00:33:10,000
Tak mahu keluar makan pula.

504
00:33:12,480 --> 00:33:13,480
Ya.

505
00:33:13,940 --> 00:33:16,480
Saya nak siapkan tulisan ini dulu.

506
00:33:17,060 --> 00:33:20,020
Baguslah awak sudah kembali fokus belajar dan menulis.

507
00:33:20,020 --> 00:33:23,400
Lebih baik daripada pergi minum dan berseronok di tempat lain.

508
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:26,260
- Kalau awak datang nak paksa saya makan...
- Bukan.

509
00:33:31,410 --> 00:33:33,270
Kalau tak mahu makan, tak apalah.

510
00:33:36,140 --> 00:33:37,540
Saya bawakan untuk awak.

511
00:33:40,450 --> 00:33:43,650
Makanlah sikit untuk alas perut, nanti sakit perut pula.

512
00:33:45,470 --> 00:33:47,650
Ini barang yang jarang ditemui.

513
00:33:52,730 --> 00:33:55,190
Di Bangkok, sekilogram hanya lebih 40 baht.

514
00:33:55,860 --> 00:33:57,500
Apa yang awak cakap tadi?

515
00:33:59,890 --> 00:34:01,880
Letak saja di situ. Nanti...

516
00:34:02,200 --> 00:34:03,440
saya kupas sendiri.

517
00:34:14,080 --> 00:34:15,810
Tangan awak kotor kena dakwat.

518
00:34:16,949 --> 00:34:18,679
Biar saya kupaskan untuk awak.

519
00:34:22,570 --> 00:34:24,570
Dah gelap, kenapa tak pasang lilin?

520
00:34:26,510 --> 00:34:28,370
Nanti sakit mata macam dulu lagi.

521
00:35:32,900 --> 00:35:34,080
Terima kasih.

522
00:35:36,700 --> 00:35:38,900
Abang minta maaf tentang hal pagi tadi.

523
00:35:42,020 --> 00:35:44,950
Abang dah melampaui batas dan terlalu masuk campur.

524
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:48,160
Harap awak jangan salahkan abang.

525
00:35:51,300 --> 00:35:52,230
Er...

526
00:35:52,820 --> 00:35:54,770
Saya pun patut minta maaf.

527
00:35:55,930 --> 00:35:57,930
Saya pun terkasar bahasa pagi tadi.

528
00:36:00,520 --> 00:36:01,470
Kenapa ketawa?

529
00:36:03,730 --> 00:36:05,220
Muka awak ada dakwat.

530
00:36:06,150 --> 00:36:08,320
Macam kucing comot.

531
00:36:11,560 --> 00:36:12,440
Mari sini.

532
00:36:12,860 --> 00:36:14,400
Biar saya lapkan.

533
00:36:17,080 --> 00:36:18,480
Er...

534
00:37:26,310 --> 00:37:27,310
Kong.

535
00:37:27,440 --> 00:37:30,080
Kenapa hembus nafas pada muka saya, awak ni kerbau!

536
00:37:30,080 --> 00:37:32,070
Awak yang pusing dan langgar saya.

537
00:37:32,110 --> 00:37:33,310
Nak kena pukul ke?

538
00:37:34,150 --> 00:37:35,480
Chuay, Kong.

539
00:37:39,310 --> 00:37:42,110
Saya suruh kalian layan Tuan Muda Klao baik-baik.

540
00:37:42,270 --> 00:37:43,800
Kalian pula yang bergaduh.

541
00:37:45,340 --> 00:37:48,150
Dah gatal badan ke? Nak kena rotan?

542
00:37:49,850 --> 00:37:51,030
Tak berani lagi, tuan.

543
00:37:51,030 --> 00:37:52,640
Hamba tak berani lagi.

544
00:38:36,470 --> 00:38:37,890
Saya...

545
00:38:40,290 --> 00:38:41,520
Saya pergi dulu.

546
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:46,070
Takut ganggu awak menulis.

547
00:38:47,250 --> 00:38:48,670
Baiklah. Eh, tak.

548
00:38:49,970 --> 00:38:51,000
Ya.

549
00:38:55,400 --> 00:38:57,200
Jangan tidur lewat sangat.

550
00:38:57,230 --> 00:39:01,000
♫ Selagi awak ada di sini ♫

551
00:39:01,030 --> 00:39:04,480
♫ Mulai sekarang dan selamanya ♫

552
00:39:04,510 --> 00:39:08,800
♫ Hargai pertemuan ini, hargai pertemuan denganmu ♫

553
00:39:08,830 --> 00:39:11,880
♫ Jadikan kewujudan saya bermakna ♫

554
00:39:11,910 --> 00:39:15,490
♫ Saya hanya minta awak tinggal di sini ♫

555
00:39:15,520 --> 00:39:18,130
♫ Memandang mata awak ♫

556
00:39:18,160 --> 00:39:21,010
♫ Saya tidak takut apa-apa pun ♫

557
00:39:21,040 --> 00:39:26,530
♫ Selagi awak ada di sisi saya, sentiasa di sisi saya ♫

558
00:39:26,560 --> 00:39:28,840
♫ Sehingga ke akhir hayat ♫

559
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:38,420
Awak urut sendiri macam ini.

560
00:39:38,850 --> 00:39:41,180
Atau suruh orang gaji urutkan untuk awak.

561
00:39:41,570 --> 00:39:43,700
Semua ini boleh bantu awak tidur lena.

562
00:39:46,920 --> 00:39:47,880
Kaew.

563
00:39:48,060 --> 00:39:49,620
Kamu datang sambung urut.

564
00:39:49,830 --> 00:39:51,010
Baiklah.

565
00:39:58,530 --> 00:40:00,960
Jangan biarkan dia berjumpa dengan orang gila lagi.

566
00:40:00,960 --> 00:40:02,570
Tak kira apa yang orang lain cakap.

567
00:40:02,570 --> 00:40:04,370
Klao akan percaya bulat-bulat.

568
00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:07,480
Keadaannya akan jadi makin teruk.

569
00:40:07,650 --> 00:40:09,210
Macam dirasuk.

570
00:40:11,940 --> 00:40:13,460
Saya pun rasa macam itu.

571
00:40:16,150 --> 00:40:18,550
Tapi jangan kurung dia dalam bilik selalu.

572
00:40:18,790 --> 00:40:21,300
Ramai banduan dalam penjara jadi gila.

573
00:40:22,310 --> 00:40:25,040
Sebab tak dapat lihat cahaya matahari dan bulan.

574
00:40:27,310 --> 00:40:28,310
Risaukan dia pun.

575
00:40:29,210 --> 00:40:30,810
Kena ada batasnya.

576
00:40:33,170 --> 00:40:34,170
Selesa betul.

577
00:40:34,980 --> 00:40:38,080
Macam buat spa telinga di Ekkamai.

578
00:40:39,550 --> 00:40:40,960
Apa yang awak cakap tadi?

579
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:43,480
Err, lupakanlah.

580
00:40:48,940 --> 00:40:52,440
Awak rasa Klao jadi macam ini sebab mabuk sahaja ke?

581
00:40:53,540 --> 00:40:56,880
Sepatutnya kalau mabuk, dia sudah sedar sekarang.

582
00:40:57,000 --> 00:40:58,600
Saya takut ada sebab lain.

583
00:41:00,410 --> 00:41:01,410
Candu ke?

584
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:05,330
Saya pun tak pasti.

585
00:41:07,640 --> 00:41:08,640
Oh ya.

586
00:41:08,880 --> 00:41:11,540
Awak tahu tak ke mana Klao pergi masa dia hilang?

587
00:41:17,100 --> 00:41:18,630
Nampaknya belum tahu lagi.

588
00:41:20,660 --> 00:41:22,820
Kalau kita dapat tahu ke mana Klao pergi masa dia hilang.

589
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:25,100
Lebih senang kita siasat apa puncanya.

590
00:41:29,950 --> 00:41:32,080
Saya gembira sangat, Abang Klao.

591
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:33,240
Hmm.

592
00:41:33,550 --> 00:41:37,010
Nampaknya awak bercakap lebih jelas berbanding sebelum ini.

593
00:41:38,050 --> 00:41:39,050
Er...

594
00:41:39,340 --> 00:41:40,340
Betul.

595
00:41:40,990 --> 00:41:43,810
Mungkin sebab saya pergi ke kuil,

596
00:41:44,030 --> 00:41:46,630
buat pahala untuk ayah saya dan mendoakannya,

597
00:41:46,760 --> 00:41:48,540
sebab itulah keadaan saya bertambah baik agaknya.

598
00:41:48,540 --> 00:41:50,200
Abang Klao dah ingat ayah?

599
00:42:00,470 --> 00:42:01,470
Hmm.

600
00:42:01,870 --> 00:42:02,870
Ya.

601
00:42:03,580 --> 00:42:04,580
Saya

602
00:42:05,010 --> 00:42:06,940
bermimpi ayah berada di mahkamah.

603
00:42:14,180 --> 00:42:16,440
Tempat itu dipanggil dewan pengadilan.

604
00:42:17,840 --> 00:42:18,840
Baguslah.

605
00:42:19,240 --> 00:42:21,100
Awak dah ingat tentang ayah awak?

606
00:42:22,890 --> 00:42:23,890
Er...

607
00:42:24,500 --> 00:42:26,030
Semua ini kerana Abang Jom.

608
00:42:26,080 --> 00:42:27,580
Nampaknya saya kena urut lebih kuat lagi.

609
00:42:27,580 --> 00:42:29,320
- Aduh!
- Tak perlu.

610
00:42:32,310 --> 00:42:35,240
Urut biasa-biasa sudahlah, tak perlu tunjuk hebat.

611
00:42:41,420 --> 00:42:42,540
Dalam mimpi,

612
00:42:43,760 --> 00:42:45,920
saya nampak ayah

613
00:42:47,280 --> 00:42:50,400
dihukum tikam dengan lembing.

614
00:42:52,790 --> 00:42:53,680
Kerana

615
00:42:56,120 --> 00:42:57,040
melakukan

616
00:42:58,230 --> 00:42:59,720
jenayah rasuah.

617
00:43:00,170 --> 00:43:01,120
Terima rasuah,

618
00:43:01,240 --> 00:43:03,100
dihukum tikam dengan lembing ke?

619
00:43:10,420 --> 00:43:12,700
Saya dengar

620
00:43:12,800 --> 00:43:14,960
orang yang macam ketua itu

621
00:43:17,460 --> 00:43:19,790
perintahkan supaya disebat di belakang.

622
00:43:20,520 --> 00:43:23,050
Sebat di belakang, maksudnya hukuman sebat.

623
00:43:28,680 --> 00:43:29,880
Disebat.

624
00:43:33,450 --> 00:43:34,400
Guna

625
00:43:36,260 --> 00:43:37,380
rotan.

626
00:43:39,970 --> 00:43:42,280
Tapi kalau ayah saya tak bersalah?

627
00:43:43,970 --> 00:43:46,230
Tapi saya percaya kata-kata Abang Klao,

628
00:43:47,850 --> 00:43:50,280
Tuan Preechapiban tak bersalah.

629
00:43:50,930 --> 00:43:52,270
Orang kampung itu

630
00:43:52,840 --> 00:43:55,040
cuma percaya kata-kata hakim.

631
00:43:56,730 --> 00:43:58,800
Sejak awak balik ke ibu kota,

632
00:43:59,260 --> 00:44:00,990
awak pergi minum setiap malam.

633
00:44:01,100 --> 00:44:04,100
Setiap malam pergi minum di hujung pasar tepi sungai.

634
00:44:04,480 --> 00:44:06,900
Awak mesti sedih sangat.

635
00:44:11,700 --> 00:44:12,910
Rupa-rupanya.

636
00:44:13,620 --> 00:44:15,150
Macam yang orang lain kata,

637
00:44:16,710 --> 00:44:18,800
kadang-kadang lebih baik tak ingat.

638
00:44:24,910 --> 00:44:27,020
Kesiannya Abang Klao.

639
00:44:28,430 --> 00:44:31,060
Hilang ingatan, sampai tak ingat hal sendiri.

640
00:44:34,620 --> 00:44:35,680
Abang Jom,

641
00:44:36,130 --> 00:44:39,440
kalau suatu hari nanti saya tak ingat awak,
macam mana?

642
00:44:41,090 --> 00:44:42,720
Tak ada apa-apa.

643
00:44:46,080 --> 00:44:47,720
Kejamnya.

644
00:44:49,170 --> 00:44:50,960
Tak ada apa-apa.

645
00:44:51,820 --> 00:44:54,020
Kalau awak betul-betul tak ingat saya,

646
00:44:54,720 --> 00:44:56,520
saya tetap akan jaga awak.

647
00:45:09,410 --> 00:45:10,720
Abang Jom.

648
00:45:12,270 --> 00:45:13,680
Saya seorang doktor.

649
00:45:14,150 --> 00:45:16,680
Walau apa pun, saya kena jaga setiap pesakit.

650
00:45:17,970 --> 00:45:19,370
Awak pun tak terkecuali.

651
00:45:30,840 --> 00:45:33,560
Maknanya, awak kasihan pada saya

652
00:45:34,300 --> 00:45:36,160
atau benci saya?

653
00:45:36,930 --> 00:45:38,100
Abang Jom.

654
00:45:51,970 --> 00:45:54,100
Pergi minum di pasar tepi sungai lagi.

655
00:45:54,680 --> 00:45:58,210
Adakah ini sebabnya
si muka ketat itu tak suka saya pergi pasar?

656
00:45:58,520 --> 00:45:59,440
Klao.

657
00:46:01,490 --> 00:46:04,290
Hal ayah awak dah berlalu, biarkanlah ia berlalu.

658
00:46:05,480 --> 00:46:06,940
Jangan fikir banyak lagi.

659
00:46:13,450 --> 00:46:15,010
Aduh.

660
00:46:15,030 --> 00:46:17,800
Tuan Muda Klao.

661
00:46:19,060 --> 00:46:22,960
Aduh, hari ini hamba susah payah dapatkan ikan besar.

662
00:46:23,040 --> 00:46:25,440
Tuan tak nak cuba sikit ke?

663
00:46:27,610 --> 00:46:29,320
Aduh, betul juga.

664
00:46:30,490 --> 00:46:32,440
Tuan Muda Klao tak makan pedas,

665
00:46:33,070 --> 00:46:35,510
tapi lauk hari ini tak pedas langsung.

666
00:46:40,350 --> 00:46:44,160
Masakan hamba rasanya tak pernah sama

667
00:46:44,190 --> 00:46:47,000
sebab hamba tak ingat resipi.

668
00:47:09,420 --> 00:47:10,980
Betul juga.

669
00:47:13,350 --> 00:47:14,880
Tak pedas langsung, Klao.

670
00:47:15,840 --> 00:47:17,240
Tapi sedap macam selalu.

671
00:47:22,260 --> 00:47:25,720
Tuan terlalu memuji hamba.

672
00:47:38,650 --> 00:47:39,840
Mengada-ada betul.

673
00:47:41,660 --> 00:47:42,320
Aduh,

674
00:47:42,460 --> 00:47:48,360
kalau tuan dapat cuba kerabu telur kerengga,
tuan mesti suka sangat.

675
00:47:48,860 --> 00:47:49,800
Telur...

676
00:47:50,430 --> 00:47:52,300
Kalau lauk itu,

677
00:47:53,250 --> 00:47:54,800
rasanya tak apalah.

678
00:48:00,060 --> 00:48:01,140
Begini.

679
00:48:01,250 --> 00:48:03,250
Suami hamba, Sorn.

680
00:48:03,300 --> 00:48:06,920
Dia pernah bawa balik sarang semut merah yang besar.

681
00:48:07,150 --> 00:48:09,640
Hamba pun buat kerabu untuk Tuan Muda Phop.

682
00:48:10,090 --> 00:48:11,950
Hamba gunakan semua kemahiran hamba.

683
00:48:11,950 --> 00:48:14,190
Sampai guna kemahiran kaki hamba sekali.

684
00:48:14,190 --> 00:48:17,680
Sambil mengacau, hamba lari ke dapur untuk minum arak ubat.

685
00:48:17,710 --> 00:48:20,120
Untuk bagi khasiat pada anak dalam perut.

686
00:48:22,860 --> 00:48:23,960
Jadi...

687
00:48:25,170 --> 00:48:26,120
Tak sedap ke?

688
00:48:26,240 --> 00:48:28,040
Aduh, sedap sangat.

689
00:48:28,080 --> 00:48:29,410
Sedap sampai tak boleh percaya.

690
00:48:29,410 --> 00:48:33,010
Masa itu, Tuan Muda Phop asyik tambah semangkuk demi semangkuk.

691
00:48:33,460 --> 00:48:34,260
Eh?

692
00:48:35,430 --> 00:48:37,360
Sampai bibir hamba pun kena gigit.

693
00:48:37,550 --> 00:48:38,560
Kena gigit bibir?

694
00:48:39,770 --> 00:48:42,320
Telur semut merah boleh gigit orang ke?

695
00:48:43,150 --> 00:48:45,370
Hamba pun ambil dan tengok betul-betul.

696
00:48:45,370 --> 00:48:47,030
Rupa-rupanya itu anai-anai.

697
00:48:59,520 --> 00:49:03,280
Puan besar marah hamba sampai hampir pengsan masa itu.

698
00:49:03,990 --> 00:49:05,680
Sepatutnya puan besar yang hampir pengsan sebab marah.

699
00:49:05,680 --> 00:49:08,760
Sebab dia marah berjam-jam lamanya.

700
00:49:08,800 --> 00:49:13,360
Tentang hamba pula, puan besar suruh orang pecahkan semua botol arak ubat hamba.

701
00:49:13,420 --> 00:49:16,080
Dan halau suami hamba, Sorn, keluar dari rumah.

702
00:49:16,350 --> 00:49:17,810
Jelas-jelas awak yang buat salah.

703
00:49:17,810 --> 00:49:19,930
Kenapa

704
00:49:20,240 --> 00:49:21,570
Sorn pula yang dihalau?

705
00:49:22,040 --> 00:49:23,690
Moto hidup hamba ialah,

706
00:49:23,720 --> 00:49:27,620
kalau buat salah jangan salahkan diri sendiri, salahkan orang lain itu lebih baik.

707
00:49:27,620 --> 00:49:29,880
Barulah hati rasa tenang.

708
00:49:42,280 --> 00:49:45,120
Aduh, tuan muda ketawa gembira hari ini.

709
00:49:45,680 --> 00:49:48,320
Sekarang boleh cuba sup ikan ini?

710
00:49:48,670 --> 00:49:52,530
Atau nak tukar dengan kerabu telur semut merah campur anai-anai itu?

711
00:50:18,080 --> 00:50:18,960
Sedap.

712
00:50:37,360 --> 00:50:38,440
Baguslah.

713
00:50:38,710 --> 00:50:41,660
Abang dah lama tak nampak awak ketawa gembira macam ini.

714
00:50:41,660 --> 00:50:46,480
Yalah, tak ada apa-apa yang kelakar pun.

715
00:50:46,610 --> 00:50:47,760
Kalau macam itu,

716
00:50:48,050 --> 00:50:50,850
nampaknya kena suruh Mak Cik Muan datang teman awak berbual setiap hari.

717
00:50:50,850 --> 00:50:53,250
Mak Cik Muan memang kelakar bila bercakap.

718
00:51:01,530 --> 00:51:02,660
Esok,

719
00:51:03,360 --> 00:51:05,070
saya nak pergi

720
00:51:05,130 --> 00:51:07,640
ikut Mak Cik Muan ke pasar terapung, boleh?

721
00:51:07,900 --> 00:51:08,790
Yalah,

722
00:51:08,900 --> 00:51:10,760
mana tahu perasaan boleh jadi lebih baik.

723
00:51:10,760 --> 00:51:13,180
Mungkin ingatan pun boleh pulih sikit.

724
00:51:18,940 --> 00:51:20,560
Saya pun nak awak pergi.

725
00:51:21,510 --> 00:51:23,310
Tapi tempat itu terlalu bahaya.

726
00:51:23,310 --> 00:51:24,450
Bahaya lagi?

727
00:51:25,690 --> 00:51:27,320
Apa yang teruk sangat dekat sana?

728
00:51:27,320 --> 00:51:29,320
Kenapa asyik cakap bahaya, bahaya?

729
00:51:33,000 --> 00:51:34,460
Awak tak jawab pun tak apa.

730
00:51:35,060 --> 00:51:36,860
Tapi kalau betul bahaya sangat,

731
